{"tid":2140911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★合體！】街市鼠患恐播疫　議員憂 肺炎+大鼠肝炎「雙炎」夾撃！","createTime":"2020-08-05T10:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T04:08:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3f7deede3e1c41e37ae67b6c8818a60b4bb8429d","tid":2140911,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:07:09.000Z","msg":"香港大學微生物學系講座教授袁國勇到兩個街市視察後指出，街市內的老鼠可能是播毒的途徑之一。惟港府滅鼠工作為人詬病，上年度花費兩億港元公帑滅鼠，但鼠患指數卻不跌反升，引入的新科技滅鼠器更淪為笑柄。有議員表示，本港踏入鼠患高峰的夏天，或會再現大鼠戊型肝炎，屆時本港恐會被雙「炎」夾擊，憂慮本港將淪為「疫城」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200805/bkn-20200805163401627-0805_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200805%2Fbkn-20200805163401627-0805_00822_001.html&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeao5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=5d99145f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200805/bkn-20200805163401627-0805_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bda01cfeb26363c9da5fd5188ddc68561cd06e9e","tid":2140911,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSiuvw4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSiuvw4.gif&h=2f73fc1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34041f98f25d621648f0018fc6bd0f7c4857d059","tid":2140911,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:09:19.000Z","msg":"HK NO ...."},{"pid":"646bb58efc982766e2cdb586ac086abd5917db36","tid":2140911,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"change getter 2 <br />\n<br />\nswitch on !"}]}